| 
| Specification of the candidate entities and optionally top-level items (e.g. Compositions)
| to be included in the Extract.
| 

class EXTRACT_MANIFEST
    is_a Any

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | List of entity manifests uids of items included in the Extract; for openEHR data, these
    | are uids identifying the version containers.
    | 
    prop entities: List<EXTRACT_ENTITY_MANIFEST>;


end
